Build dependencies (on Debian):

	make
	m4
	flex
	bison
	libtool
	libtool-bin
	libgmp-dev
	libreadline-dev
	texlive
	ghostscript

To build and test:

	make
	make test	# builds first if necessary

To build a subdirectory (e.g. lc):

	make nop	# at top level; creates subdir Makefiles
	cd src/lc
	make
